OL,3,CPolice appeal for information into
OL,4,Cdeath of man from a sailing boat
OL,6,FDorset Police are appealing for
OL,7,Finformation following the death of a
OL,8,Fman in Poole Harbour.
OL,10,FOfficers received a report on Sunday,
OL,11,F31 May that a man was believed to have
OL,12,Fgone into the water from a sailing
OL,13,Fboat in the area of Arne Bay on
OL,14,FFriday, 29 May.
OL,16,FOn Tuesday, 2 June, a body was
OL,17,Frecovered from the water off the coast
OL,18,Fof Baiter Park.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
