CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780650345
OL,3,CPolice appeal for information into
OL,4,Cdeath of man from a sailing boat
OL,6,FWhile formal identification has not
OL,7,Fyet taken place, it is believed to be
OL,8,Fthe man who was reported to have gone
OL,9,Finto the water ` 35-year-old Michael
OL,10,FMitchell from Chelmsford in Essex, who
OL,11,Fwas known to his family as 'Mitch'.
OL,13,FHis family is being kept informed with
OL,14,Fdevelopments in the investigation.
OL,16,FThree men have been arrested on
OL,17,Fsuspicion of murder ` a 46-year-old
OL,18,Ffrom Poole, a 31-year-old of no fixed
OL,19,Fabode and a 22-year-old from Essex.
OL,20,FThey are all known to Michael Mitchell.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
