PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780650345
OL,3,CPolice appeal for information into
OL,4,Cdeath of man from a sailing boat
OL,6,FDorset Police's Major Crime
OL,7,FInvestigation Team says the arrests
OL,8,Fwere made to assist the investigation
OL,9,Fin gathering information and also to
OL,10,Fprovide legal protection to those
OL,11,Finvolved as enquiries continue.
OL,13,FA forensic post mortem has been
OL,14,Fcarried out but the cause of death has
OL,15,Fyet to be confirmed and further
OL,16,Fdetailed testing and analysis is
OL,17,Frequired.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
