PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780650345
OL,3,CPolice appeal for information into
OL,4,Cdeath of man from a sailing boat
OL,6,FAll of the three men who were arrested
OL,7,Fhave now been released on police bail
OL,8,Fas further investigative work is
OL,9,Fconducted.
OL,11,FDetective Chief Inspector Nicky
OL,12,FJenkins, of MCIT, said: "Our detailed
OL,13,Fenquiries to establish the full
OL,14,Fcircumstances of this death remain
OL,15,Fongoing and we are continuing to keep
OL,16,FMichael Mitchell's family fully
OL,17,Fupdated.
