PN,41305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780650345
OL,3,CPolice appeal for information into
OL,4,Cdeath of man from a sailing boat
OL,6,F"I would again appeal for anyone with
OL,7,Finformation that might assist our
OL,8,Fenquiries to please come forward,
OL,9,Fincluding anyone who had any contact
OL,10,Fwith Mr Mitchell in the days leading
OL,11,Fup to Friday 29 May 2026."
OL,13,FAnyone with information is asked to
OL,14,Fcontact Dorset Police online or by
OL,15,Fcalling 101.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@ZO]
